Package: EasySC
Type: Package
Title: Easy Single-Cell RNA Sequencing Analysis Pipeline
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mating", "Chenyong", email = "1962140509@qq.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: A streamlined and user-friendly pipeline for single-cell RNA
    sequencing (scRNA-seq) data analysis. EasySC wraps popular Bioconductor
    and CRAN packages (Seurat, Harmony, scDblFinder, scCDC, etc.) into a
    cohesive workflow, providing one-step functions for quality control,
    normalization, batch correction, clustering, doublet removal, and
    ambient RNA decontamination. 
